OL,3,CThames Valley Police working hard to
OL,4,Crebuild public trust, says Chief
OL,5,CConstable
OL,7,F"There is no doubt that when a high
OL,8,Fprofile incident happens anywhere in
OL,9,Fthe country, it affects how people see
OL,10,Fthe police here in the Thames Valley,"
OL,11,Fsaid Hogg. "People don't see the
OL,12,Fboundaries of police forces."
OL,14,FHe has set out a vision for the police
OL,15,Fforce to be 'excellent', and is
OL,16,Fworking with a private sector
OL,17,Forganisation to ensure that happens.
