OL,3,CThames Valley Police working hard to
OL,4,Crebuild public trust, says Chief
OL,5,CConstable
OL,7,F"We will focus our attention on
OL,8,Fimproving trust and confidence every
OL,9,Fyear, because if people don't trust
OL,10,Fthe police, they won't report crime,
OL,11,Fprovide statements or stand up in
OL,12,Fcourt."
OL,14,FIt comes as 2023-24 statistics have
OL,15,Fbeen released by the force. Hogg has
OL,16,Fpraised the progress on knife crime
OL,17,Fand sexual violence.
