OL,3,CThames Valley Police working hard to
OL,4,Crebuild public trust, says Chief
OL,5,CConstable
OL,7,FKnife crime is down 11% which the
OL,8,FChief Constable says is because of
OL,9,Ftheir continued use of the
OL,10,F'controversial' stop and search
OL,11,Fmethods as well as early prevention.
OL,13,FRape charges are up 17% and other
OL,14,Fsexual offences are up 13% on the year
OL,15,Fbefore. Hogg says driving down
OL,16,Fviolence against women and girls has
OL,17,Fbeen a huge priority and he's really
OL,18,Fproud of the work being done in that
OL,19,Farea.
