OL,7,FOverall arrests have also risen by 6%
OL,8,Fhighlighting what they say is a
OL,9,Ftougher approach to crime.
OL,11,FThe Chief Constable said there could
OL,12,Fbe a "real risk across the country"
OL,13,Fthat police officers "don't have
OL,14,Fconfidence to use their powers."
