OL,3,CThames Valley Police working hard to
OL,4,Crebuild public trust, says Chief
OL,5,CConstable
OL,7,FHe said many of his officers report
OL,8,Fthat the public record their
OL,9,Finteractions with officers on their
OL,10,Fmobile phones, particularly in
OL,11,F"polarised" debates. But he said
OL,12,Fofficers do have confidence to use
OL,13,Ftheir powers.
OL,15,F"We are an outlier that 'stop and
OL,16,Fsearch' continues to rise in the
OL,17,FThames Valley," said Hogg. "It gives
OL,18,Fconfidence to me that officers do feel
OL,19,Fthey are supported."
