OL,3,CThames Valley Police working hard to
OL,4,Crebuild public trust, says Chief
OL,5,CConstable
OL,7,FDrug trafficking is up a quarter on
OL,8,Flast year. 1671 incidents were
OL,9,Frecorded in the past year, with Jason
OL,10,FHogg saying he is 'reassured about
OL,11,Fdrug crime trafficking' having taken
OL,12,Fover 150 guns off the streets - more
OL,13,Fthan ever before.
OL,15,FAs of March 2024, 48% of his staff is
OL,16,Ffemale but only 5% overall are from
OL,17,Fethnic minority communities - versus a
OL,18,Fpopulation of around 14%.
